Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:08.00,Default,,0,0,8,,{\blur3\fn华文楷体\fs18}影片压制：风潇潇　字幕调校：风潇潇　招募Q号：76846146{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.31,0:01:45.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今年因为五黄临太岁 周围都有旱灾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.81,0:01:47.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有旱灾的地方就有麻烦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.07,0:01:50.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有麻烦 我就有生意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.94,0:01:53.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是西域白驼山人士{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.28,0:01:55.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我名叫欧阳峰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.36,0:01:57.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的职业 就是帮人解决麻烦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.08,0:02:02.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看来你的年纪应该四十出头{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.42,0:02:06.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这四十几年来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:11.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你应该有些事是不想再提 或是有些人你不想再见{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.76,0:02:13.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有的人曾经对不住你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:18.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或者你想过 想杀了他们{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.02,0:02:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过你不敢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.85,0:02:29.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又或者你觉得不值得{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.44,0:02:36.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实杀人 好容易的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.12,0:02:41.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有个朋友 他的武功非常好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.74,0:02:44.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过最近生活有点问题{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.71,0:02:50.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要你随便给他一点银两 他一定可以帮你杀了那个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:55.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你尽管考虑一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.84,0:02:58.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实杀一个不是很容易{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:01.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过为了生活{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.26,0:03:03.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好多人都会冒这个险{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.77,0:03:05.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}离开了白驼山之后{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:07.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去了一个沙漠{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}开始另外一种生活{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.86,0:03:21.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}初六日 惊蛰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.66,0:03:25.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每年这个时候 都会有一个人来找我喝酒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.54,0:03:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他的名叫黄药师{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.87,0:03:29.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个人好古怪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.96,0:03:32.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每次都是由东边来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.42,0:03:35.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个习惯已经维持了好多年{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:38.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}今年 他带了一份手信给我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.51,0:03:45.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不久之前 我遇到一个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.85,0:03:50.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她送一坛酒给我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.52,0:03:56.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她说叫"醉生梦死"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.19,0:04:01.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}人喝了之后 无论以前做过的什么都可以忘记{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.74,0:04:05.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我好奇怪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.50,0:04:08.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么有坛这样的酒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.75,0:04:15.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她说 人最大的烦恼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.71,0:04:19.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是记性太好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.51,0:04:21.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果可以所有的事都忘记{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.72,0:04:25.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以后的每一日都有个新的开始{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:27.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你说这有多开心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.35,0:04:34.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这坛酒本来打算带来送给你的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.69,0:04:39.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看上来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:42.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们要分来喝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.87,0:04:49.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对于太古怪的东西 我向来很难接受{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.42,0:04:54.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以这一坛"醉生梦死" 我始终都没喝到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.92,0:04:59.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或者真是有效{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.76,0:05:05.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那晚黄药师 开始不记得好多事情{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.31,0:05:12.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还记不记得我们是怎样认识的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.11,0:05:18.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我 不是好记得{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.61,0:05:22.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你还记不记得你是怎样来这里的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.07,0:05:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我都不是好记得{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.24,0:05:29.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么你老望着那鸟笼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.75,0:05:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为 很眼熟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.52,0:06:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能他喝得太醉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.98,0:06:42.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第二天清早就走了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.19,0:06:44.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知他有什么烦恼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能同一个女人有关系{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.87,0:06:57.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个月之后 黄药师去了一个好远的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.46,0:07:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那里是他一个好朋友的故乡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:05.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他的朋友结婚那年{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.34,0:07:07.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}黄药师曾经在那儿住过一段时间{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.72,0:07:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没多久 他朋友离开了家里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.85,0:07:18.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那次以后 黄药师也都没再回过那个地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.61,0:09:30.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不介意请你喝杯酒吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.78,0:09:33.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我今晚只是想喝水{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.72,0:09:57.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我们以前有没见过{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.81,0:10:01.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不止见过{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.89,0:10:05.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你曾经是我最好的朋友{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:08.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过现在已经不是了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.57,0:10:16.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你来这儿做什么{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.45,0:10:20.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之前我碰到一个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:24.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她送一坛酒给我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.08,0:10:29.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她说喝了之后 无论以前做过什么都会不记得{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:32.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我试过{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很有效{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.09,0:10:38.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知你有没有兴趣试哈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.14,0:10:44.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知不知喝酒跟喝水的分别{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.35,0:10:48.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}酒会越喝越暖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.69,0:10:52.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}水会越喝越寒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.04,0:11:05.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还会不会在这里见到你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.91,0:11:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不会{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:14.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我曾经发过誓 如果再让我见到这个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.05,0:11:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定会杀了他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.55,0:11:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是我没这样做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.72,0:11:23.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我见他的时候 眼睛已经看不见东西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.39,0:11:25.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你到底是男还是女{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.27,0:11:34.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}堂堂大燕国的公主{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.15,0:11:36.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}慕容家的小姐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.40,0:11:39.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你竟敢如此冒犯我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.99,0:11:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}信不信我杀了你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.96,0:11:52.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你喝醉了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.30,0:12:46.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}年青时候的黄药师 是一个放荡不羁的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.27,0:12:51.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他很容易让人家喜欢他 也很容易伤害到人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.11,0:12:57.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那晚 黄药师差点死在一个人的手上边{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:14.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每年总有几个月 人们好像不愿死似的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.25,0:13:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去年立春之后 我一直没开过张{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.55,0:13:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}整个月 只有一个人来找我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.55,0:13:24.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想要你帮我杀一个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:27.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他的名字叫黄药师{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.02,0:13:30.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他是当今数一数二的剑客{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.43,0:13:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我怕不是很容易杀死他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.02,0:13:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要可以杀了他 我不惜任何代价{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.44,0:13:39.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过我有个条件{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:41.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他一定要死在我手上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.61,0:13:44.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}而且是最痛苦的死法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:46.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么你跟他这么大仇怨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.17,0:13:55.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为一个女人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.08,0:13:57.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他抛弃了我的妹妹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:05.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他的名叫名叫做慕容燕 他自称是慕容公子的后人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.26,0:14:09.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她同黄药师在姑苏城外的桃花林一见如故{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.39,0:14:11.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那天是 初四 立春{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.06,0:14:13.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}黄历上面写着{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:15.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"东风解冻"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.52,0:14:17.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是说 是一个新的开始{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.52,0:14:22.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有一晚 黄药师跟他开了一个玩笑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.19,0:15:06.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你有个妹妹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:08.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定会娶她为妻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.88,0:15:23.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:26.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那我们就一言为定{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.55,0:15:29.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你千万别后悔{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.39,0:15:31.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你后悔的话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.81,0:15:34.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定会杀了你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.06,0:15:41.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之后 他们定了个日子 约在一个地方见面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.40,0:15:44.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结果黄药师没去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.75,0:16:47.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我哥哥是不是来找过你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.59,0:16:49.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你哥哥是哪位{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.80,0:16:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他的名字叫慕容燕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.97,0:16:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他好象来过{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.60,0:16:58.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他是不是要你帮他杀一个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.27,0:17:00.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不记得了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.14,0:17:03.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你真敢杀了他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:07.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定会要你死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.65,0:17:11.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你哥哥出手阔绰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.78,0:17:15.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不答应他 是不小的损失{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.66,0:17:20.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这个年头 这么舍得花钱杀人的人 不是很多哦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.83,0:17:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只要你不答应他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.13,0:17:27.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我可以付你双倍来补偿你的损失{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.05,0:17:31.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过 我有一个条件{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:34.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你要你帮我杀一个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:37.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他就是我哥哥 慕容燕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.68,0:17:42.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你两兄妹的感情真是好怪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.85,0:17:45.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你真的这么憎恨你哥哥{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.81,0:17:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}对{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.36,0:17:51.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为他不让我和黄药师在一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:54.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他觉得我是属于他的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.36,0:17:56.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以 他一定要死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.17,0:18:10.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我妹妹是不是来找过你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.38,0:18:12.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.05,0:18:15.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要对她有非份之想{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.68,0:18:17.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}否则我连你都杀了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.89,0:18:19.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你都挺关心你妹妹的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.06,0:18:22.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她是我唯一的亲人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.14,0:18:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只不过是想保护她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.39,0:18:25.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她来找你做什么{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.77,0:18:27.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她叫我帮她杀一个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.32,0:18:33.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他名叫慕容燕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.57,0:18:39.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定是黄药师教她这样做的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.95,0:18:42.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算没黄药师 她都会这样做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.79,0:18:45.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她要离开你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.75,0:18:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不会让她离开我的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.08,0:18:50.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}除非我死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.94,0:19:14.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你今天去见过我哥哥{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:19.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他告诉你听的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.95,0:19:22.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么还不动手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.54,0:19:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我怕我收不到钱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.71,0:19:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实杀你哥 是一件好易的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:34.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为他有弱点{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.38,0:19:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道是什么吗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.18,0:19:38.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.47,0:19:48.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我告诉他 要杀他的人是你 就是想看一下他的反应{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.65,0:19:53.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然他反对你和黄药师在一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.65,0:19:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能因为他喜欢你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:19:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果是的话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.86,0:20:01.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喜欢你到什么程度{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.37,0:20:03.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他要我一生一世跟他在一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.66,0:20:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那他真的喜欢你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.37,0:20:08.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道他很喜欢我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.83,0:20:11.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可惜我不喜欢他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.63,0:20:13.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我喜欢的人是黄药师{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.17,0:20:16.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那他不是很伤心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:18.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就让他伤心去吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:21.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然我这么不开心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.85,0:20:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么不找一个人陪我呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.35,0:20:29.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就是要他尝尝得不到一个人的滋味{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.89,0:20:32.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你都很残忍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:33.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不怕他死吗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.82,0:20:35.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就是要他死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.57,0:20:40.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么你会跟我说这些{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.37,0:20:44.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你哥哥问过我一个问题{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想了很久 终于被我想到了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.41,0:20:50.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要一个人死 最痛苦的方法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.54,0:20:53.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是先杀了他最喜欢的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.25,0:20:56.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是我不可以这样做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.17,0:20:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我杀了你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.13,0:21:00.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我找谁收钱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.93,0:21:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是不是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:40.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有人要追杀我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.10,0:21:47.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无缘无故 为什么会有人追杀你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.35,0:21:53.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们说我是黄药师最喜欢的女人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.94,0:21:58.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要让他们杀了我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.32,0:22:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那晚 那个女人一直都不肯走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.61,0:22:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我看见她这么惊慌 就给她喝了一点酒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.95,0:22:10.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之后 她就睡着了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.33,0:22:16.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你把我妹妹藏到哪里去了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.71,0:22:18.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么你这么肯定我收留了她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.75,0:22:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道她曾经来找过你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.63,0:22:25.01,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之后就没有人再见过她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.39,0:22:29.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有一晚 她来找我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.26,0:22:31.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她说她被追杀 叫我收留她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.98,0:22:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之后就走了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.64,0:22:36.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她不是回了家吗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.11,0:22:39.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我妹妹跟人无仇无怨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.11,0:22:43.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}无缘无故怎么会有人要追杀她呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.40,0:22:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像说 因为她是黄药师最爱的女人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.07,0:22:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}笑话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.03,0:22:51.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他要是喜欢她的话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.70,0:22:53.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么要离开她呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.21,0:23:01.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有些人是离开后{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.42,0:23:04.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才会发觉那个人是最喜欢的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.59,0:23:09.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也许黄药师就是这种人呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.35,0:23:11.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他不是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.14,0:23:15.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你为什么这么肯定{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.40,0:23:24.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为他已经喜欢上另外一个女人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.99,0:23:31.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个人受到挫折 或多或少会找个借口来掩饰自己{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.99,0:23:38.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实慕容燕 慕容嫣 只不过是一个人的两个身份{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.04,0:23:43.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在这两个身份的后面 躲藏着一个受了伤的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.71,0:23:45.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你喝醉了 慕容兄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.97,0:23:47.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}慕容兄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.39,0:23:53.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你认错人了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.14,0:23:56.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不是什么慕容兄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.35,0:23:59.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我乃是堂堂大燕国的公主{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.06,0:24:03.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}慕容家的小姐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.98,0:24:05.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的名字叫慕容嫣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.57,0:24:10.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你究竟是什么人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.62,0:24:13.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不认得我了吗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.17,0:24:26.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你曾经说过要娶我为妻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.67,0:24:29.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我又怎么会不认得呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.72,0:24:34.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有说过这样的话吗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.06,0:24:37.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当日你作客姑苏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.69,0:24:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我和你在桃花树下饮酒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.61,0:24:45.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你借醉 摸着我的脸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.57,0:24:47.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}说{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.86,0:24:49.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我有个妹妹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:50.03,0:24:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一定娶她为妻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.12,0:24:57.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你明知道我是女儿之身{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.83,0:24:59.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么要这样做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.75,0:25:05.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}喝醉之后说的话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.63,0:25:07.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你又怎可以这么认真呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.38,0:25:12.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为你的一句话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.68,0:25:15.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直等到现在{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.60,0:25:19.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我曾经要你带我走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.81,0:25:21.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是你没有这样做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.06,0:25:26.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你说 你不能同时喜欢两个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:26.82,0:25:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你喜欢的那女人是慕容嫣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.49,0:25:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你为什么又喜欢另外一个女人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.33,0:25:40.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知不知道我曾经去找过那个女人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.96,0:25:51.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为有人说你最喜欢的女人是她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.59,0:25:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我本来想杀了她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:54.97,0:25:57.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}后来我没有这样做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.60,0:26:00.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我不想证明她就是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.36,0:26:08.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我曾经问过自己{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.07,0:26:11.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你最喜欢的女人是不是我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.91,0:26:18.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在我已经不想再知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.25,0:26:24.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果有一天我忍不住问起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.08,0:26:25.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你一定要骗我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.92,0:26:28.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就算你的心有多么不愿意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.05,0:26:32.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不要告诉我你最喜欢的人不是我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.77,0:26:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那晚过得特别长{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.40,0:26:50.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我好象同时在跟两个人说话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.23,0:26:52.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也分不清{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.78,0:26:54.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到底是慕容燕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.61,0:26:56.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是慕容嫣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.79,0:27:08.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}慕容燕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.01,0:27:13.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}慕容嫣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.30,0:27:18.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}告诉我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.22,0:27:21.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你最喜欢的女人是哪一位{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.27,0:27:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不就是你咯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.65,0:27:32.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前也有人这样问过我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.44,0:27:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是我没有回答{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.11,0:27:36.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}换了是黄药师的身份{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.03,0:27:40.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我觉得这几个字 原来并不是很难说出口{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.76,0:27:56.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那晚睡觉的时候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.92,0:27:58.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我又感觉到有人摸我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.01,0:29:30.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道她想摸的人不是我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.85,0:29:36.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她只不过当我是另外一个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.15,0:29:38.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实我又何尝不是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:40.74,0:29:42.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她的手很暖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.16,0:29:46.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就跟我大嫂的手一样{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.31,0:30:55.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}由那晚开始 就再没人见过慕容燕或是慕容嫣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.40,0:31:00.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}几年之后 在江湖出现了好奇怪的剑客{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.11,0:31:02.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没人知道他的来历{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.94,0:31:06.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只是知道 他喜欢对着自己的倒影练剑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.78,0:31:09.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他有一个特别的名 叫独孤求败{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.56,0:32:18.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你找我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.94,0:32:22.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想找个人帮我弟弟报仇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.69,0:32:25.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他发生了什么事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:27.70,0:32:30.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}几日前 有一班刀客经过我家门口{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.24,0:32:36.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我弟弟他年少无知 得罪了其中一个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.37,0:32:40.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们就将他杀死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.38,0:32:46.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}官府不管吗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:47.63,0:32:50.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为他们是太尉府的刀客{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.47,0:32:53.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}官府都不敢追究{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:56.77,0:32:58.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你出得起多少钱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.64,0:33:03.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我家里很穷 根本就没有什么多余的钱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.94,0:33:09.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只剩下这篮鸡蛋 同一只驴子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:12.99,0:33:16.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这只驴子 是我娘生前留给我的嫁妆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.83,0:33:23.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你真有心为你弟弟报仇的话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:24.92,0:33:26.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我劝你筹一笔钱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.92,0:33:32.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有人会为了一只驴子 得罪太尉府的刀客{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.68,0:33:35.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}报仇也要代价{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.97,0:33:40.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是你长得难看{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.81,0:33:43.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我劝你死了这条心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.15,0:33:47.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你千万不要以为我对你有什么企图{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.98,0:33:50.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只是想告诉你 如果要卖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.70,0:33:55.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你会比那驴更加值钱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.70,0:33:58.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你明白我的意思吗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.66,0:34:02.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不会这样做的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.96,0:34:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你嫌钱少{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.67,0:34:07.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我会一直在这等{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.96,0:34:10.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想一定会有人肯帮我的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.14,0:34:20.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道她是不是真的要为弟弟报仇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:20.72,0:34:23.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还是没事可干{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.03,0:34:38.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从这里看下去 她好像一个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.90,0:35:12.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}接着的几晚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.28,0:35:14.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我都做了同一个梦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.24,0:35:19.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我梦见我家乡的桃花开了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.91,0:35:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我忽然间想起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.79,0:35:26.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来我已经有好多年 没回去过白驼山了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.87,0:36:06.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你的眼睛有事吗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.62,0:36:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自小我的眼睛就不好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.79,0:36:13.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大夫说我三十岁就会看不见东西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.17,0:36:16.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你今年贵庚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.67,0:36:18.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}刚刚三十岁{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.22,0:36:23.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你还来干什么{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.14,0:36:28.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每年的春天 家乡的桃花都会开得很灿烂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.85,0:36:33.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想在我失明之前 回去再看一次{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.15,0:36:37.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可惜身上的盘缠已经用完了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.32,0:36:39.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听人讲 你专门帮别人解决麻烦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.74,0:36:41.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知可不可以帮到我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.08,0:36:47.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}几个月之前 我有个朋友在这里杀了一批马贼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.50,0:36:51.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听说马贼的兄弟最近会回来找他报仇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.00,0:36:53.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可惜我那个朋友已经走了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.55,0:36:58.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}附近的人担心会殃及池鱼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.17,0:37:01.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以愿拿一笔钱出来 找个高手杀了他们{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.02,0:37:09.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听说这一带有一个人的刀很快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.85,0:37:11.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道他在不在{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.56,0:37:13.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你找他干什么{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.06,0:37:16.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想看看是他的刀快 还是我的剑快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.20,0:37:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我根本不应该来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.03,0:37:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太迟了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.04,0:37:27.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}留只手行吗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.75,0:37:29.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.62,0:37:32.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要留 留下你的命{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:57.32,0:37:59.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你误会了我的意思{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.82,0:38:03.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说我不应该来 是因为你根本不是我的对手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.61,0:38:05.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我说留只手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.91,0:38:08.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁知你却要把命送给我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.50,0:38:20.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你可不可以帮我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.60,0:38:30.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他虽然是一个落泊的剑客{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.02,0:38:33.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但他的生活很有规律{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.10,0:38:37.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每天都会来这里喝一杯酒 吃两碗饭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.48,0:38:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}到太阳下山的时候 他就会走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.18,0:39:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你为什么老看着那个女人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.64,0:39:14.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为她使我想起另一个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.31,0:39:16.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你老婆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.15,0:39:24.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然这么想她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.15,0:39:26.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又何必四处飘泊呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.24,0:39:32.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她爱上了我最好的朋友{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.33,0:39:40.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知那帮马贼什么时候到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.17,0:39:45.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}大概就这一两天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.68,0:39:49.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}希望他们快点到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.89,0:39:53.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要是太迟回去的话 桃花都谢了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.62,0:40:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}花什么时候开是有季节的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.16,0:40:18.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}马贼什么时候到 却没有人知{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:20.33,0:40:23.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他每天在城外等{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.13,0:40:25.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我发现他越等越晚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.47,0:40:34.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然他晚晚都点一盏油灯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:34.14,0:40:37.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我知道 他夜晚是看不见东西的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.30,0:41:14.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是不是不喜欢我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.56,0:41:24.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你很想回家乡去吗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.15,0:41:29.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.61,0:41:32.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你结婚没{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.62,0:41:34.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么这么问{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.45,0:41:39.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我猜你一定很喜欢你老婆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:40.50,0:41:42.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以这么说{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.42,0:41:45.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然这样 为什么不留在她身边{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.70,0:42:14.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可以再请我喝碗酒吗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:26.59,0:42:29.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你今晚这么有兴致{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:33.97,0:42:36.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我怕明天晚上没机会再喝了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.14,0:42:45.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想他们{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.10,0:42:46.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天亮时才会到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.48,0:42:50.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我帮你准备好了灯笼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.15,0:42:53.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}现在有没有灯笼 对我来讲根本不重要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.28,0:42:59.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你已经看不到东西了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.83,0:43:03.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}太阳猛烈还能看见{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.00,0:43:06.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}希望明天天气会好一点{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.04,0:43:10.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果日落后还不见我回来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.71,0:43:13.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}麻烦你帮我找一个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.38,0:43:15.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他的名字叫黄药师{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:18.47,0:43:21.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}告诉他我家乡还有一个人在等他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.40,0:44:12.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道为什么会这样做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:13.03,0:44:15.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我控制不了自己{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.61,0:44:18.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我走的时候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.16,0:44:21.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那女人的眼泪在我脸上慢慢干了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.71,0:44:35.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道那个女人会不会为我流泪呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.10,0:49:41.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我以前听人讲 如果刀够快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:41.44,0:49:45.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}血从伤口喷出来的时候 像风声一样 好好听{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.53,0:49:49.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想不到第一次听到的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.53,0:49:52.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是我自己流出来的血{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.34,0:50:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这人的名字叫洪七{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:52.63,0:50:55.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他的刀很快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.26,0:50:57.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但他不喜欢穿鞋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.35,0:50:59.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道他可以帮我赚很多钱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.76,0:51:02.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是我一直都不喜欢这个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.31,0:51:04.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我命书中有一句话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.60,0:51:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尤忌七数 是以命终{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.15,0:51:12.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我第一次见到他时 他刚从乡下出来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.87,0:51:19.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}知不知道为什么我请你吃饭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.66,0:51:21.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:21.37,0:51:23.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我知道你肚子饿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.00,0:51:27.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实我注意你很久了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.88,0:51:31.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我看见你蹲在那座破墙下半天也没动过{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:31.80,0:51:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看你又不像是生病{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.88,0:51:37.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你这种年青人我见的多了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.01,0:51:41.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}懂一点武功就以为可以横行天下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:43.14,0:51:45.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实行走江湖是一件很痛苦的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.73,0:51:49.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会武功 有很多事不能做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:50.73,0:51:52.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不想耕田{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.69,0:51:54.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又不耻去打劫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.82,0:51:57.49,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}更加不想抛头露面在街头卖艺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.57,0:51:59.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那你怎么生活{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.08,0:52:03.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}武功高强都要吃饭的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.50,0:52:07.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实有一种职业很适合你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.08,0:52:09.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既可以帮你赚点银两{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.83,0:52:12.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又可以行侠仗义 不知你有没有兴趣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:13.76,0:52:15.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就这样吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.34,0:52:17.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}尽管考虑一下 不过要快哦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.38,0:52:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道 肚子很快就会饿的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.44,0:52:38.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}洪七来了没多久{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.11,0:52:40.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}上次那群马贼又回来了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.24,0:52:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在我带他去见那群村民之前{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.04,0:52:46.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我帮他买了一双鞋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.54,0:52:51.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为有穿鞋的和不穿鞋的刀客 价钱相差很远{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.63,0:53:01.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么 你们觉得十两银子这价钱很贵吗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.27,0:53:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那么你们可以找几个便宜的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.48,0:53:10.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那边有几个{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.77,0:53:12.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没穿鞋子的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.31,0:53:15.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你给他几两银子 他们都很开心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:18.11,0:53:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但如果这个人连鞋都没有穿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:21.45,0:53:23.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你对他有信心吗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.08,0:53:34.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}万一他们失手了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:34.50,0:53:37.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}让那帮马贼知道是你们指使的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.51,0:53:40.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你想那帮马贼会怎么对付你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.34,0:53:47.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不敢说我这位朋友 武功比他们都好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.43,0:53:49.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我现在跟你们说的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.37,0:53:52.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是你们一家大小二十多条人命的安全{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:53.61,0:53:55.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}至少在这方面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.69,0:53:58.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你们该信一个穿鞋的人的人 是不是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.86,0:54:01.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了不想重蹈覆辙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.20,0:54:03.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我带洪七去了一个地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.78,0:54:05.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你带我看死尸干什么{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.62,0:54:07.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为死尸会说话的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.62,0:54:11.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}两天前 他想在这里伏击马贼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.37,0:54:13.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以为可以杀光他们{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:14.04,0:54:16.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁知死的是他自己{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.50,0:54:19.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}取他性命的 是这一刀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.22,0:54:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}很明显跟其它伤痕很不同{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.43,0:54:26.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}是从右至左{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.22,0:54:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他全身只有一个刀伤{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:28.89,0:54:34.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也就是说 其中有一个人 只不过出了一刀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.60,0:54:36.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是这一刀 要了他的命{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:39.94,0:54:42.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以你对付这群马贼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.70,0:54:45.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要留意一个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.20,0:54:47.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一个用左手拿刀的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.25,0:54:53.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我死了 你不用带人来看我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.25,0:54:57.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不想做一条会说话的死尸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:58.04,0:55:02.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}十五日 晴 有风{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.26,0:55:05.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}地官降下 定人间善恶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.72,0:55:08.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有血光 忌远行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.47,0:55:10.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宜诵经解灾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.40,0:57:27.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}通常拿了钱看也不看 就收起来的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:27.40,0:57:29.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他们的钱很快就会花光{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.41,0:57:35.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但洪七他数得很仔细{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:35.12,0:57:38.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这种人 我知道 不会留在我身边太久{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.75,0:57:49.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}初十日 立秋 晴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.92,0:57:53.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}凉风至 宜出行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:53.59,0:57:55.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会友 忌新船下水{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:57.43,0:57:58.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}洪七{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:59.27,0:58:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他走了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.56,0:58:05.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我想他不会回来了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.77,0:58:07.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不如你到别的地方找他吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:22.79,0:58:24.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你明不明白我说什么{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.14,0:58:37.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}别以为要欺骗一个女人是很容易的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.47,0:58:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}越是单纯的女人就越直接{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:40.98,0:58:44.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她知道她丈夫根本没有离开{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.31,0:58:47.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为洪七是不会抛下他的骆驼不理的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:57.66,0:59:00.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我叫你在乡下等我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.41,0:59:03.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你老跟着我干啥 啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.00,0:59:05.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:05.83,0:59:06.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:09.42,0:59:10.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不回克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.67,0:59:14.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你回克吧 回克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.51,0:59:16.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}回克{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.85,0:59:23.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.43,0:59:26.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赶快走 走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.21,0:59:46.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那个女人在外面等了你好几天了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.75,0:59:49.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赶她走她都不肯走 我有什么办法呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:49.75,0:59:52.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}难道要我带着老婆闯荡江湖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:54.63,0:59:56.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没说不行啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.76,0:59:59.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}事在人为嘛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.43,1:00:07.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我曾经好象你一样{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.48,1:00:10.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一心打天下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.90,1:00:13.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以为能抛下自己的女人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.82,1:00:19.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁知等我回到家 才发觉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.78,1:00:24.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她变成我大嫂了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.55,1:00:36.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你天天来找我也没用{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.55,1:00:41.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你没钱 我也帮不了你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.10,1:00:44.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你还是回去 想想别的办法吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:47.18,1:00:48.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我求求你了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.06,1:00:50.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你求我没用{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:52.23,1:00:54.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只不过是一个中间人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.57,1:00:58.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要求的人 是你自己{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.42,1:01:15.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每个人都会为一些东西而坚持{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.55,1:01:17.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其他人会觉得是浪费时间{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.01,1:01:21.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但对这个人来讲 却很重要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:33.23,1:01:36.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}十五 有雨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.11,1:01:38.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}土黄用时{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.32,1:01:40.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}曲星{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.11,1:01:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}宜沐浴 忌出行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.95,1:01:45.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冲龙煞北{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.41,1:03:08.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我是那群太尉府的刀客{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:08.83,1:03:11.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一定会死不瞑目{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.20,1:03:14.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}原来这么多条命加起来 只不过值一个鸡蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.87,1:03:18.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为了一个鸡蛋而失去了一只手指 值得吗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.63,1:03:26.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不值得{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.01,1:03:30.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我觉得痛快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.18,1:03:34.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这才是我自己{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.44,1:03:41.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}本来我应该没事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.57,1:03:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是我的刀没以前快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.87,1:03:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我以前快是因为我直接{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:51.95,1:03:54.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}觉得对就去做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.29,1:03:57.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从来不会想什么代价{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.88,1:04:02.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我以为我这一辈子都不会变{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.88,1:04:06.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直到那个女孩来求我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:08.14,1:04:11.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我才发觉我自己完全变了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.18,1:04:16.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我竟然没有答应她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.27,1:04:20.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我知道你一定不会答应{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.69,1:04:27.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那天 我好失望{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:31.24,1:04:34.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我觉得我自己和你混在一起 变成一个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.12,1:04:38.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有了自己{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.09,1:04:43.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不想跟你一样{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.68,1:04:51.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我知道欧阳峰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:51.89,1:04:55.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}绝对不会因为一个鸡蛋去冒险{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.35,1:05:00.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这是我和你的分别{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.92,1:05:25.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你能不能救救洪七{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:32.01,1:05:34.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听说他病得很厉害{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.97,1:05:38.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}能不能请个大夫 看看他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.27,1:05:39.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}请大夫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.89,1:05:41.60,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}要钱的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.44,1:05:45.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可惜我家没有鸡蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.44,1:05:48.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果有 我可以给你几只{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.61,1:05:52.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知道 你最擅长用鸡蛋请人做事的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.79,1:06:05.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是不会救他的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:06.21,1:06:08.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为他不听我的话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.67,1:06:11.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实 他搞成这样 都是因为你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:13.43,1:06:15.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不如你去救他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.85,1:06:21.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道你不到山穷水尽是不会来求我的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.35,1:06:25.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在这儿等着你来求我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.65,1:06:31.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我记得你讲过 你说不愿意为别人牺牲自己{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.78,1:06:36.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我看你这次 会不会讲得出做得到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.88,1:06:46.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你在想什么{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:46.25,1:06:47.54,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没什么{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.51,1:06:54.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不要为我做任何事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.84,1:06:57.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我这次真的死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.72,1:07:03.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我也会死的好开心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.02,1:07:10.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我帮你是为了那鸡蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:12.86,1:07:14.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}鸡蛋我已经吃了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:17.49,1:07:19.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你没欠我什么{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.16,1:07:24.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}记住 别做傻事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.67,1:07:32.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}之后{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.30,1:07:35.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就没再见过那个女人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.03,1:08:02.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能我以后不会再用刀吃饭了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.87,1:08:08.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不一定要用刀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:08.88,1:08:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}赤手空拳都可以杀死人的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.42,1:08:15.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你不过是少了根手指 这也没什么{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.97,1:08:18.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好歹还有份差事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.84,1:08:20.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}怎么{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.35,1:08:21.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}想回家乡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.06,1:08:24.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你这样就想着回家乡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.52,1:08:26.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么当初你又要出来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:28.44,1:08:30.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知过了这个沙漠 后面是什么地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.90,1:08:32.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}还不就是另外一个沙漠{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.53,1:08:37.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每个人都会经过这个阶段{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.28,1:08:41.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}见到一座山 就想知道山后面是什么{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.74,1:08:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我很想告诉他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:43.33,1:08:46.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能翻过去 你会发觉没什么特别{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:46.29,1:08:47.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}再翻过来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:48.04,1:08:50.50,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}会觉得这边更好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.58,1:08:52.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我知道他不会听{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.88,1:08:54.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以他的性格{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.42,1:08:57.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自己不走一走 又怎么会甘心呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:06.02,1:09:07.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你打算去哪儿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.77,1:09:09.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}去一个我没去过的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.31,1:09:10.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}希望可以闯出个名堂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:10.98,1:09:13.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你以后在江湖上听说一个九指英雄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.69,1:09:15.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那一定是我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.19,1:09:16.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那她呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.90,1:09:20.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}带她一起 像你说的 事在人为嘛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.03,1:09:25.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}又没规定说不准带老婆闯荡江湖 对不对{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.91,1:09:28.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.91,1:09:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我终于明白那个女人为什么会喜欢洪七{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.00,1:09:34.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能是因为他够简单{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.21,1:09:38.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看着他们走的时候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.51,1:09:40.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的心在妒忌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.18,1:09:44.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}曾经我也有过这样的机会{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.30,1:09:46.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知为什么{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.39,1:09:48.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我却放弃了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:35.52,1:10:39.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他走的那天 风是向南面吹的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.61,1:10:43.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他故意逆风而行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:43.53,1:10:45.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我记得那一天是十五{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.87,1:10:47.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}黄历上写着{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:48.04,1:10:52.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}失星当值 大利北方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:09.89,1:11:13.39,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}洪七走了之后 天一直在下雨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.10,1:11:17.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每次下雨 我就会想起一个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.44,1:11:20.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她曾经很喜欢我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:23.57,1:11:26.28,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道是不是巧合{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:26.41,1:11:28.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每次我要离开她远行的时候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.03,1:11:30.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}天都会下雨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.58,1:11:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她说是因为她不高兴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.79,1:11:37.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}后来她嫁给了我哥哥{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.88,1:11:39.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她结婚那天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.80,1:11:42.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我就离开了白驼山{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.86,1:12:51.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你就算明天再问我 答案还是一样 我不跟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.03,1:12:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你跟不跟我走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.83,1:12:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你也不会好过{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:56.54,1:13:01.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不跟 你记住 从今天开始 我就是你嫂子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.38,1:13:04.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以后可以拉我手的人只有一个 就是你哥哥{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:04.46,1:13:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其他的人没有资格{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.84,1:13:46.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你为什么老看着我的汗巾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:47.51,1:13:50.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这条汗巾是我丈夫的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.18,1:13:52.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么会在你这里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:12.24,1:14:14.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他是不是已经死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.79,1:14:20.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能因为太久没看过桃花了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.46,1:14:24.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}第二年的春天 我去了那个人的家乡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.25,1:14:26.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我很奇怪那里{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:26.92,1:14:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}根本就没桃花{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.10,1:14:42.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这件东西对我来说已经没用了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.11,1:14:49.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在我离开的时候 才知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.36,1:14:53.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这地方根本就没桃花{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:54.78,1:14:57.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}桃花 只不过是一个女人的名字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:19.47,1:15:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}听到那个女人的哭声{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:21.98,1:15:26.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我突然间明白 为什么黄药师每年都来探望我一次{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:38.28,1:15:40.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你觉不觉得他好奇怪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:41.33,1:15:43.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也不理人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.50,1:15:49.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}悄无声息{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:49.17,1:15:52.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}分明心里想要 嘴巴却不肯讲出来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:55.26,1:15:57.59,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一定要你送到面前才肯要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:03.77,1:16:06.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最初想 由着他吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.94,1:16:11.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}渐渐地也就不想迁就他了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:11.15,1:16:15.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然我很喜欢她 但是我始终都不想让她知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.70,1:16:19.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我知道 得不到的东西永远是最好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.62,1:16:22.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每次她凝望着那小孩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:23.04,1:16:25.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道她心里其实在想另一个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.00,1:16:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我很妒忌欧阳峰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.67,1:16:33.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我很想知道被人喜欢的感觉是怎样的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:34.21,1:16:36.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结果我伤害了很多人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.18,1:16:42.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直都以为你们会在一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:43.06,1:16:45.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么你不嫁给他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.98,1:16:52.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他从没说过他喜欢我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.65,1:16:55.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有些话不一定要说出来的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:16:57.53,1:17:00.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我只需要他说一句话而已{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.70,1:17:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但他都不肯说{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.20,1:17:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}他太自信了 以为我一定会嫁给他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.75,1:17:13.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}谁知道我嫁给了他哥哥{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.92,1:17:20.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在我们结婚那晚 他要我跟他走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.76,1:17:22.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我没答应{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:27.43,1:17:30.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么要到失去的时候 才去争取{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:31.86,1:17:33.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}既然是这样{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:33.69,1:17:36.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不会让他得到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.28,1:17:38.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果感情是可以分胜负的话{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:38.57,1:17:41.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我不知道她是不是赢了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.24,1:17:43.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我很清楚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.62,1:17:46.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从一开始 我就是输的那个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:51.96,1:17:55.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是因为这个女人才喜欢桃花{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:55.13,1:17:58.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每年桃花开的时候 我都能见到她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.05,1:18:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我去探望欧阳峰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.30,1:18:05.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为她想知道欧阳峰的消息{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.31,1:18:08.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}也因为欧阳峰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.81,1:18:12.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我每年都可以有借口去看她一次{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.65,1:18:17.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你知不知道 现在对我来说什么最重要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:20.49,1:18:24.11,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果我没猜错的话 应该是你的儿子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:26.49,1:18:28.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我以前也是这么想对{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.08,1:18:33.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是看着他一天天长大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:35.75,1:18:38.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道他早晚会离开我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.34,1:18:45.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我觉得什么都无所谓了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.52,1:18:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前我认为那句话很重要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:57.36,1:19:02.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为我觉得有些话说出来 就是一生一世{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.37,1:19:08.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是现在想一想{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.83,1:19:13.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实说不说也没有什么分别{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:15.67,1:19:17.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为有些事会变的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:27.01,1:19:29.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直都以为是我自己是赢的那个{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:33.39,1:19:35.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}直到有一天看着镜子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:40.07,1:19:43.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}才知道自己输了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:45.49,1:19:48.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为在我最美好的时候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.87,1:19:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我最喜欢的人都不在我身边{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.92,1:20:03.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果可以重新开始 那该多好啊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:00.02,1:21:02.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实你跟他这么要好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.95,1:21:09.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}为什么不告诉他我在这里呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.95,1:21:12.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我答应过你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.28,1:21:15.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}所以我一直都没说{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:21.50,1:21:23.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你太老实了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.06,1:23:06.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没多久 她就病死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:08.23,1:23:13.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在她临死之前 她交给我一坛酒 要我带给那个人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:15.91,1:23:19.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}她希望欧阳峰可以忘记她{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:23.29,1:23:28.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有人说 一个人有烦恼 是因为记性太好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:30.38,1:23:33.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}从那年开始 我忘记了很多事情{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:36.05,1:23:39.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}唯一有印象的 就是我喜欢桃花{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.92,1:24:12.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}立春之后 很快就又到了惊蛰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.05,1:24:16.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}每年这个时候 会有位朋友来探我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.05,1:24:19.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但是他今年没有来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:39.32,1:24:43.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没多久 我收到一封白驼山来的信{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.75,1:24:50.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为一场大病 我大嫂在两年前的冬天去世了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.34,1:24:57.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道黄药师不会再来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:57.72,1:24:59.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可是我还继续等{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.64,1:25:03.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我在门口坐了两天两夜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.39,1:25:07.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}看着天空在不断的变化 我才发现{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.39,1:25:10.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}虽然我到这里很久{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:10.19,1:25:13.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但我却从来没看清楚过这片沙漠{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.53,1:25:20.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}以前看见山{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:20.49,1:25:23.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就想知道山的后面是什么{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.49,1:25:25.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}但现在 我已经不想再知道了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.50,1:25:29.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我是个孤星入命的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.83,1:25:32.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}父母很早就死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:32.38,1:25:35.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}只有跟哥哥相依为命{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.25,1:25:37.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可能因为是孤儿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.80,1:25:40.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我很小就懂得应该怎样去保护自己{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.47,1:25:45.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我知道 如果你不想被人拒绝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.97,1:25:48.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}最好的方法 就是先拒绝别人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:49.19,1:25:51.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}因为这个原因{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:51.81,1:25:54.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我一直都没再回去过{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:54.77,1:25:57.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实那边也不错{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.11,1:25:59.44,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}可惜我已经不能回头了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.28,1:26:05.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我的命书里说 "夫妻宫 太阳化忌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:05.83,1:26:09.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}婚姻有实无名" 想不到是真的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.41,1:26:47.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那晚 我忽然之间很想喝酒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.54,1:26:50.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}结果我喝了那半坛"醉生梦死"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:51.91,1:26:55.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}好像平常一样 我继续做我的生意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:26:59.13,1:27:02.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}老兄 看来你已经四十出头了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.72,1:27:07.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}这四十几年来{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:08.06,1:27:11.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}总有些事你不想再提 或有些人你不想再见{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:13.81,1:27:15.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}有个人可能很对不起你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:17.11,1:27:19.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}或者你想过杀了他们{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:22.45,1:27:24.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过你不敢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.87,1:27:31.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实 杀一个人是很容易的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:32.12,1:27:34.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}一点也不麻烦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:34.29,1:27:37.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我有个朋友 他武功非常好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:38.25,1:27:40.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过最近生活上有点困难{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.76,1:27:46.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果你能给他一点钱的话 他一定可以帮你杀了他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:51.39,1:27:52.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}考虑一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:54.14,1:27:56.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不过要快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:56.10,1:27:57.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}如果不是的话…{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:27:59.94,1:28:04.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}没有事的时候 我会望向白驼山{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.62,1:28:10.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我清楚的记得 曾经有一个女人在那边等着我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:16.33,1:28:21.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}其实"醉生梦死" 只不过是她跟我开的一个玩笑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.09,1:28:26.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你越想知道自己是不是忘记的时候{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.79,1:28:28.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你反而记得更加清楚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.76,1:28:33.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我曾经听人说过{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:33.52,1:28:38.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}当你不能够再拥有的时候 你唯一可以做的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.44,1:28:41.31,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}就是令自己不要忘记{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:49.12,1:28:52.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不知道为什么 我老是做着同一个梦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:28:53.70,1:28:57.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不久 我就离开了这个地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:18.35,1:29:20.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}离开那天 黄历上写道:{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:29:20.73,1:29:26.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\blur3}"驿马动 火逼金行 大利西方"{\r}
